<p><h2 class="size"><a href="javascript:showHide('div8')" style="color:grey">2. What is the internet connection requirement for smooth working of Bank or DRT Auctions?</a></h2></p>


<div id="div8" style="display:none;padding-left:20px">
<p align="justify" style="color:black; font-size:13px; font-family:arial">
It is recommended to have an uninterrupted internet connection with speed of 256 KBPs or higher; please remember during the Auction process internet connection should not go off.</p>
</div>


<p><h2 class="size"><a href="javascript:showHide('div9')" style="color:grey">3. What format of documents can be uploaded? And up to what size?</a></h2></p>


<div id="div9" style="display:none;padding-left:20px">
<p align="justify" style="color:black; font-size:13px; font-family:arial">
Auctioneer can upload .ppt, .doc .pdf, .xls, .jpg and .zip files. There is a size limit of 2 MB for each document. Only one document can be uploaded for a particular field. In case, multiple documents are required to be uploaded, bidder can upload a single zip file containing multiple documents.</p>
</div>
<p><h2 class="size"><a href="javascript:showHide('div1')" style="color:blue">Precautions:</a></h2></p>
<div id="div1" style="display:none;padding-left:20px">
<p align="justify" style="color:black; font-size:13px; font-family:arial">
1)	One user / bank login should be done in one browser.<br>
2)	If the user tries to login with another credential in the same browser but in other tab, it may lead to issues. So use only one tab of one browser.<br>
3)	If there are any issues in the auction/bidding screen, please refresh and check if everything is fine (username, auction details, etc). If not, please logout and relogin.<br>
4)	Sometimes the above issue comes due to the browser cache issue. So it is always better to clean/clear the cache.
</p>

